COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 7:30AM PT today, over 1.3 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 24.6 thousand have died.

In the last day, 681 new infections were reported and 6 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 16.1 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 44.6% have their 1st shot and 3.8% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 2.1 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~8 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Jul-05 and fully vaccinated by Aug-30. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
